{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require labels on all products showing water and carbon usage in manufacture",
        "additional_details": "There is an environmental impact for every product we buy. This is having a detrimental impact on public health, species diversity and climate. In turn this harms crops, economies, living standards/stability. Through eco-labels we will: \r\n1 Put pressure on manufacturers to adopt more eco-friendly practices; \r\n2 Empower consumers to make choices which balance personal need with responsibility; \r\n3 Balance economic prosperity with the environment for the long term benefit of life and planet",
        "background": "Just as we have nutritional information, alcohol volume and energy consumption ratings on product - we ask that manufacturers add a label to indicate how much water and carbon went into the manufacture of a product in the form of a clear and easy to understand rating for consumers.",
